\c 3
\s VaIsraeri vanoyambuka Joridhani
\p
\v 1 Zvino Joshua wakamuka mangwanani-ngwanani; zvino vakabva paShitimi ndokusvika paJoridhani, iye nevana vaIsraeri vose, ndokurarapo vasati vayambuka\x + 2.1.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino zvakaitika pakupera kwemazuva matatu\x + 1.11.\x* kuti vatariri vakagura nepakati pemusasa\x + 1.10.\x*,
\v 3 ndokuraira vanhu vachiti: Kana muchiona areka yesungano yaJehovha Mwari wenyu, nevapristi VaRevhi vakaitakura, ipapo imwi muchabva panzvimbo yenyu ndokuitevera\x + 2.8. Num.. 10.33. Det. 31.9,25. 17.18.\x*.
\v 4 Asi pachava nenzvimbo pakati penyu nayo, makubhiti anenge zvuru zviviri nechiyero; musaswedera kwairi, kuti muzive nzira yamungaenda nayo; nokuti hamuna kupfuura nenzira iyi zuro \add na\add*marimwezuro\x + Eki. 19.12.\x*.
\v 5 Zvino Joshua wakati kuvanhu: Zviitei vatsvene, nokuti mangwana Jehovha achaita zvinoshamisa pakati penyu\x + Eki. 19.10,14,15. Rev. 20.7. Num.. 11.18. Josh. 7.13. 1 Sam. 16.5. Jow. 2.16.\x*.
\v 6 Joshua ndokutaura nevapristi achiti: Simudzai areka yesungano mugopfuura mberi kwevanhu. Zvino vakasimudza areka yesungano ndokufamba mberi kwevanhu\x + Num.. 4.15.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Joshua: Nhasi ndichatanga kukukudza pameso aIsraeri wose\x + 4.14. 1 Makor. 29.25. 2 Makor. 1.1.\x* kuti vazive kuti sezvandaiva naMozisi ndichava newe\x + 1.5.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino iwe ucharaira vapristi vanotakura areka yesungano uchiti: Kana masvika pamucheto wemvura yaJoridhani\x + 3.3.\x*, muchamira muna Joridhani\x + 3.17.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Zvino Joshua wakati kuvana vaIsraeri: Swederai pano, mugonzwa mashoko aJehovha Mwari wenyu.
\v 10 Joshua ndokuti: Muchaziva neichi kuti Mwari mupenyu ari pakati penyu\x + Hos. 1.10. Det. 5.26. 1 Sam. 17.26. 2 Madz. 19.4. Mat. 16.16. 1 VaTes. 1.9.\x*, uye kuti achadzinga zvirokwazvo\x + Vato. 11.24.\x* pamberi penyu\x + Eki. 13.5.\x* VaKenani neVaHiti neVaHivhi neVaPerezi neVaGirigashi neVaAmori neVaJebhusi.
\v 11 Tarirai, areka yesungano yaShe wenyika yose inopfuura mberi kwenyu muna Joridhani\x + 3.13. Mik. 4.13. Zek. 4.14. 6.5. Det. 9.3.\x*.
\v 12 Naizvozvo ikozvino zvitorerei varume gumi nevaviri kubva pamarudzi aIsraeri\x + 4.2,4.\x*, murume parudzi rumwe nerumwe\x + Num.. 13.2.\x*.
\v 13 Zvino zvichaitika apo pasi petsoka dzevapristi vanotakura areka yaJehovha\x + 3.15,16.\x*, Ishe wenyika yose, padzinozorora mumvura yaJoridhani, mvura yaJoridhani ichagurwa, mvura inoburuka kubva kumusoro\x + 3.13. Mik. 4.13. Zek. 4.14. 6.5. Det. 9.3.\x*; ichamira ive murwi umwe\x + Eki. 15.8; Map. 114.3.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Zvino zvakaitika vanhu vachibva pamatende avo kuyambuka Joridhani, vapristi vakatakura areka yesungano mberi kwevanhu\x + Mab. 7.45.\x*.
\v 15 Neapo avo vakatakura areka vakasvika paJoridhani, netsoka dzevapristi vakatakura areka dzichinyikwa pamucheto wemvura\x + 3.13.\x* (nokuti Joridhani rwunozara mhenderokedzo dzarwo\x + 1 Makor. 12.15. Jer. 12.5. 49.19. 50.44.\x* dzose mazuva ose egoho\x + 4.18. 5.10,12.\x*),
\v 16 kuti mvura yaiburuka kubva kumusoro yakamira ndokusimuka kuita murwi umwe, kure-kure neguta reAdhama riri kurutivi rweZaretani\x + 1 Madz. 4.12. 7.46. Vato. 7.22. 1 Madz. 11.26.\x*; neyaienda pasi kugungwa rebani\x + Det. 3.17.\x*, gungwa remunyu, yakapera kugurwa; vanhu ndokuyambuka pakatarisana neJeriko\x + Gen.. 14.3.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino vapristi vakatakura areka yesungano yaJehovha vakamira pavhu rakaoma pakati paJoridhani vakasimba, Israeri wose ndokuyambuka pavhu rakaoma, kusvika rudzi rwose rwapedza kuyambuka Joridhani\x + Eki. 14.29.\x*.